name: YangGang
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: yang gang
des:
Welcome to the Yang Gang Skill! Listen to insightful quote spoken by Andrew Yang during his 2020 presidential campaign.

Just say "Alexa, open Yang Gang", and a quote spoken by Andrew Yang will be played. Once the quote is complete you will be asked if you want to hear another quote. New quotes are added daily.
